# Main problem trigger (LOCKED)

**SSOT:** `data/sourcea-main-problem-trigger-v1.json`  
**Activate:** `python3 scripts/main_problem_trigger_v1.py --activate --text "<founder message>" --json`  
**Flag:** `~/.sina/main-problem-trigger-active-v1.flag`

## Trigger phrases

Founder says: **main problem** · **main real task** · **whole thread** · **north star** · **what is the main problem**

## One law

> **PREPARE the next bounded action on the north star — do not write a report.**

## North star (main problem)

**Agentic trust infrastructure → market traction** via **cloud-first factories**:
- Phase 0: **Noetfield freemium** → **TrustField sandbox** on **Railway/cloud** (OpenRouter — not local Ollama)
- **Mac = control panel only** (Hub · form · observe)
- **Official form** (`/form/`) batch submit → nerve cascade on disk

## When triggered — agents MUST

1. Run `main_problem_trigger_v1.py --activate --text "<founder message>" --json`
2. Read receipt `next_action` + `disk_snapshot`
3. **Execute** that bounded action (WORK) — or state **one** blocker with proof
4. Reply shape: **Problem (1 line) · blocker · what I do next** — max 3 sentences

## When triggered — agents MUST NOT

- Long status reports · validator dumps · language-rule theater
- Mac cleanup unless founder asked Mac/heat
- Docs/sidebar-only when cloud or form is the blocker
- Invitation CTAs to founder

## Forbidden substitute

Reporting PASS/FAIL lists is **not** preparing. Preparing = **next disk action chosen and started**.
